data.description: This Effingham County home offers quick access to all the conveniences of Pooler. The amenity rich Stone Gate Community is just moments from I-16, GA-204 and I-95, offering quick access to HAAF, GA Port Authority, Savannah Hospitals and SCAD.  A picturesque community with a single entry point, lighted sidewalks and well maintained common areas make for a peaceful place to call home.  Whether you unwind with a neighborhood stroll or you prefer the community pool or hot tub, Stone Gate has something for everyone.
